text: The president of Somaliland is the head of state and head of government of Somaliland. The president is also commander-in-chief of the Somaliland Armed Forces. == List of officeholders == ; Political parties ; Symbols Died in office Portrait Name Elected Term of office Political party Took office Left office Time in office 1 Abdirahman Ahmed Ali Tuur 1991 28 May 1991 16 May 1993 SNM 2 Muhammad Haji Ibrahim Egal 1993 1997 16 May 1993 3 May 2002 Independent UDUB 3 Dahir Riyale Kahin 2003 3 May 2002 27 July 2010 UDUB 4 Ahmed Mohamed Mohamoud 2010 27 July 2010 13 December 2017 Kulmiye 5 Muse Bihi Abdi 2017 13 December 2017 Incumbent Kulmiye ==References==
